item.title: Swiss Fintech Website
item.description:
Here you can add additional context, description, links, etc. The content you see here comes from the contents of the content/projects folder.

This project is in the file projects/swiss-fintech.md.

In the markdown file frontmatter you can also define additional parameters, such as the link:

link: "https://www.adrianmoreno.info" # optional URL to link the logo to

params:
    button:
        icon: "icon-arrow-right"
        btnText: "Case Study"
        URL: "https://www.adrianmoreno.info"
    image:  
        src: "images/works/swissfintech.jpg"
        scale: 0.5
